OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GUK long range forecast
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wed 17 Jun to Wed 1 JulFThe
OL,6,Fstart of the period is likely to be
OL,7,Frelatively settled, with high pressure
OL,8,Fin the vicinity of the UK bringing
OL,9,Fdrier conditions to most parts of the
OL,10,FUK. However some showers or spells of
OL,11,Frain are still possible. Winds will
OL,12,Fmostly be light with temperatures
OL,13,Fprobably above normal. Towards the end
OL,14,Fof June, low pressure may begin to
OL,15,Fhave more of an influence, especially
OL,16,Facross the south where heavy showers
OL,17,Fand thunderstorms become more
OL,18,Fprobable. It may also become hot in
OL,19,Fparts of the south.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
